    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pot (with a lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion </strong>and <strong>chopped potato </strong>to the pot with the <strong>chopped tomato</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Cook for 4-5 min or until the onion is beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1687533758085-x200.jpg",
