            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>creamed coconut</strong> (if required!)</p><p>Crush the <strong>cardamom pods</strong> open by squashing them with the side of a knife</p><p>Discard the <strong>outer green pods</strong> and add the <strong>cardamom seeds</strong> to the pot with the <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, <strong>curry powder </strong>and <strong>ground turmeric</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for a further 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1687533762805-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1687533762805-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
