            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1687533762805-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1687533762805-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and 550ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> to the pot and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until the potato is fork-tender</p><p>Once the potato is fork-tender, blitz until smooth with a <strong>(stick) blender </strong>–<strong> </strong>this is your <strong>Goan-stye curry soup</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1687533766855-x200.jpg",
