      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Goan-style haddock soup</strong> in bowls, taste for seasoning, adding more <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> if needed</p><p>Top with most of the <strong>tomato chilli chutney</strong>, a little drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a crack of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>warmed naans</strong> to the side and any <strong>remaining tomato chilli chutney</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
